{"tid":924523,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊急）基督徒入一入","createTime":"2018-12-02T07:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T03:34:09.000Z","uid":11506,"like":28,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b77113a29ef200c15daac4c227a14ea17dfe02c6","tid":924523,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:19:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落地獄啦你班柒頭"},{"pid":"9e72f8c27686e20a0bbfc638c51427e07d7313ca","tid":924523,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:20:41.000Z","msg":"駁吾刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9d93efb121e2faa1b2048f7e96cc3f688e476a","tid":924523,"uid":11506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T08:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8387510edf5dd2f35652dbcd9fcabc83dd35e7fe","tid":924523,"uid":39044,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:48:21.000Z","msg":"點原因咁討討厭基督徒?.?"},{"pid":"5159f580bd2c96cec01e150af79a1acce118ab68","tid":924523,"uid":3874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:25:57.000Z","msg":"ok入咗"},{"pid":"598fb6272fda87b173b46c297ec370db733700f7","tid":924523,"uid":121701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:27:55.000Z","msg":"So?"},{"pid":"349a9908d2d5fe64f7f9fe2c9c084c7b89b8ae22","tid":924523,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97dd27a57f57f055d8c268a4ba8be7f5fcb7d42f","tid":924523,"uid":216127,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:30:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d124c38a4333914a018d4d279b5c19139a6da65","tid":924523,"uid":61832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:43:21.000Z","msg":"想問下班愛国耶撚對於我国修改聖經有咩睇法？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國近年對境內基督徒進行大規模迫害，不僅強制拆毀十字架、禁止家庭教會，網路聖經甚至被下架。美國舊金山一名牧師日前公開表示，中國政府將重新編訂《聖經》，其中會加入儒家、道家及佛家經典，並在註釋本中體現愛黨愛國的「社會主義價值觀」。<br />\n<br />\n根據《新唐人》先前報導，大陸各大電商下架《聖經》的主要原因是中共要重新翻譯出版《聖經》，編寫《聖經》註釋。大陸的基督徒現在要購買《聖經》，只能從中共的三自教會購買，以後大陸人只能買到中共版本的《聖經》了。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國《自由亞洲電台》報導，美國舊金山「華人基督徒公義團契」創辦人劉貽牧師，日前公開演說時表示，中國政府新編的《中華基督教聖經》將加入儒家、道家及佛家經典篇章，註釋部分則會引入愛國、愛黨思想，以體現社會主義核心價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n劉貽牧師指出，中國政府近年大力迫害境內基督徒，從關閉教堂、拆除十字架到抓捕無辜牧師及徹查家庭教會，當局目的在推行「基督教中國化」，這也包含重新編訂中國版聖經。<br />\n<br />\n劉貽牧師表示，在重新編訂和注釋《聖經》的同時，中共推行&ldquo;基督教中國化&rdquo;，將全面改造基督教，包括實行&ldquo;教堂中國化&rdquo;，意圖將教堂改建成如同佛教的廟宇&ldquo;靈修中國化&rdquo;，要求基督徒&ldquo;聖經論語對讀&rdquo;等。（吳雯淇／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"220674825ec2c5b423ddc4467647ec7a5509c71b","tid":924523,"uid":11506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5159f580bd2c96cec01e150af79a1acce118ab68","tid":924523,"uid":3874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:25:57.000Z","msg":"ok入咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"落地獄啦"},{"pid":"9001eb84914c649743b75c6e79374b9ca175bf57","tid":924523,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T10:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a374ab7fd7fcb245f5eaa123c930c0026f26aee9","tid":924523,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}